===Verb===
{{en-verb|misses the boat|missing the boat|missed the boat}}

# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To [[fail]] to take [[advantage]] of an [[opportunity]]; to [[overlook]] or be too [[late]] to pursue an [[option]] or [[course of action]].
#: ''The price discount ended yesterday and I just '''missed the boat''' on a great deal.''

